12-0.query:
SELECT MIN(cn.name) AS movie_company, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating, MIN(t.title) AS drama_horror_movie
FROM cat_company_name_1 AS cn,
 cat_company_type_1 AS ct,
 cat_info_type_1 AS it1,
 cat_info_type_1 AS it2,
 cat_movie_companies_1 AS mc,
 cat_movie_info_1 AS mi,
 cat_movie_info_idx_1 AS mi_idx,
 cat_title_1 AS t
WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id
 AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
 AND mi.info_type_id = it1.id
 AND mi_idx.info_type_id = it2.id
 AND t.id = mc.movie_id
 AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
 AND cn.id = mc.company_id
 AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
 AND mc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
 AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
AND cn.country_code = '@param0'
AND ct.kind = '@param1'
AND it1.info = '@param2'
AND it2.info = '@param3'
AND mi.info IN ('@param4')
AND mi_idx.info > '@param5'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN @param6 AND @param7;

Due to its violence, the film was originally threatened with an "X" rating by the MPAA''s (Motion Picture Association of America) newly created Production Code Administration, but an "R" rating was its final decision. The film was restored to its original "director''s cut" length of 143 minutes and threatened with an NC-17 rating when submitted to the MPAA ratings board in 1993 prior to a re-release in 1994, holding up the film''s re-release for many months. The reinstated scenes (including two important flashbacks from Pike''s past, and a battle scene between ''Pancho Villa (I)'' (qv)''s rebels and Gen. Mapache''s forces at the telegraph station) depicted the underlying character and motivations of the leader of the Bunch.

SYUXTUN is an American Indian term meaning ''where the road divides''. For the past five years, Paul and his friend Jake have been searching every weekend for his girlfriend Emma up on the SYUXTUN trail head. Something has been calling Paul to keep returning and this weekend he and Jake find more than they bargained for. While searching, three more campers arrive with issues of their own. Each of their lives start down another path after crossing SYUXTUN. Who will survive? This amazing docudrama was written, acted out and filmed by students from the WIA Youth Employment Program and filmed in Atascadero, CA and the students interject their filming experience and philosophy on horror movies between scenes.', 'Based in the 1660''s of London''s theaters, this film is about the rules of gender roles in theatre production, and means to change them for everyone''s benefit. Ned Kynaston is the assumedly gay cross-dressing actor who has been playing female parts in plays for years, particularly Desdemona in Othello, he also has a close relationship with a member of the Royal Court, the Duke of Buckingham. One day however, the rules of only men playing women could change when aspiring actress Maria auditions as Kynaston''s praised role, Desdemona, and soon enough, King Charles II decides to make the law that all female roles should be played only by women. Maria becomes a star, while Ned finds himself out of work. But after a while, Ned finds it in his nature to forgive Maria''s aspiration, they may even fall in love, and Charles may proclaim women will be played by either gender.', 'Ellie Andrews: I''ll stop a car, and I won''t use my thumb!::Peter Warne: What''re you gonna do?::Ellie Andrews: It''s a system all my own.', 'Germany:28 December 1945', 'DEM 5,000
